law.history: Repealed and reenacted as KRS 194A.365, 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 99, sec. 33, effective June 20, 2005; and repealed ch. 99, sec. 674, effective June 20, 2005. -- Created 1998 Ky. Acts ch. 426, sec. 47, effective July 15, 1998.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Annual report on committed children -- Contents.
metadata.lrc-note: (6/20/2005). Pursuant to KRS 446.260, the repeal and reenactment of this statute in 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 99, sec. 33, prevails over its repeal in 2005 Ky. Acts ch. 99, sec. 674.
